title: Divorce? we can help! Real estate problems solved!
posting_body: ['Are you going through a divorce and interested in selling or buying a home?', 'We can help!', 'My name is Steve and I am a licensed Realtor with Bridge Realty in Bloomington.', 'I have helped several people going through a divorce.', 'If you are thinking about selling a property and have questions, I have the experience to help you through this process.', 'Please send me an email with your phone number and email address, and I will respond as soon as possible, you can also call me at:', 'show contact info', '.', 'Here is a link to my website to learn more about what we do:', '<URL>', 'If your property is now listed with a REALTOR or Broker, please disregard this offer, as it is not our intention to solicit the offerings of other REALTORS or Brokers.']
